data.description: Welcome Home! Located in one of Dayton's premier neighborhoods, this home has so much to offer. 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, an oversized backyard with access to FM 1008, 2 dining/breakfast areas and tall ceilings. With so much storage to offer, this home is perfect. 45 minutes to downtown Houston or 45 minutes to Beaumont this location is key to escaping the big city. Schedule your showing today!
